Output docs/src/wizard.gif
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 850
Set Height 600
Set Padding 20
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set TypingSpeed 50ms

Hide
Type "cargo build -p zarrduck > /dev/null 2>&1"
Enter
Type "clear"
Enter
Show

Type "./target/debug/zarrduck plot ../../analysis.duckdb"
Enter
Sleep 2s
Enter
Sleep 1s
Space
Down
Space
Enter
Sleep 1s
Enter
Sleep 3s
